This project is a simple and interactive Mini Calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
It performs basic arithmetic operations such as addition, subtraction, and multiplication.
The user enters two numbers through input fields provided on the webpage.
Buttons are used to select the desired operation.
The interface is designed using HTML for structure and CSS for styling and layout.
The design is clean, centered, and user-friendly for easy interaction.
JavaScript is used to handle user inputs and perform calculations.
Event listeners detect button clicks and trigger the respective operations.
The result is displayed instantly on the screen without refreshing the page.
The project demonstrates basic concepts like DOM manipulation and event handling.
